      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " مَثَلُ الْبَنَفْسَجِ فِي الدُّهْنِ كَمَثَلِ شِيعَتِنَا فِي النَّاسِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Isa, from Usman Bin Isa, from Khalid Bin Najeeh, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘An example of the violet (oil) among the oils is like an example of our<sup>asws</sup> Shias among the people’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "10. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn ‘Isa from ‘Uthman ibn ‘Isa from Khalid ibn Najih who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘The likeness of viola oil among the oils is like our followers among the people.’” "
        ]
      }
